snippet.title: Surviving Mars Green Planet Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
The Green Planet expansion will give players the power to turn the Red Planet green with terraforming elements, alongside a host of other improvements to the core gameplay.
Find out more: https://pdxint.at/2UvmKfH
